'''沙長城'''（Great Wall of Sand），是[[美國太平洋艦隊|美國太平洋艦隊]][[司令|司令]][[哈里·B·哈里斯|哈里·B·哈里斯]][[海军上將|海军上將]]於2015年3月31日在[[澳洲|澳洲]]訪問時提出的新名詞，意指[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]]在[[南海爭議|南海爭議]][[南海諸島|地區諸島]]進行大規模[[填海|填海]]建造[[人工島|人工島]]的行為<ref name=香港蘋果日報>{{cite news|title=【南海局勢】美海軍將領：中國創建「沙長城」|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20150331/53589224|accessdate=2015-05-22|newspaper=[[香港蘋果日報|香港蘋果日報]]|date=2015-03-31|archive-date=2015-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150504181641/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20150331/53589224|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中國政府在此有[[領土糾紛|領土糾紛]]的區域開展了其稱之為「開荒」的一系列項目，他們抽取[[砂|砂石]]至[[珊瑚礁|珊瑚礁]]的周圍，興建包括軍事設施在內的永久性建築，比如在[[永暑礁|永暑礁]]上的3000[[公尺|公尺]][[跑道|跑道]]<ref>{{Cite web |title = China's first runway in Spratlys under construction |url = http://www.janes.com/article/50714/china-s-first-runway-in-spratlys-under-construction |website = IHS Jane's 360 |accessdate = 2015-05-22 |date = 16 April 2015 |last = Hardy |first = James |last2 = O'Connor |first2 = Sean |archive-date = 2015-05-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150526004631/http://www.janes.com/ARTICLE/50714/CHINA-S-FIRST-RUNWAY-IN-SPRATLYS-UNDER-CONSTRUCTION |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title = China 'building runway in disputed South China Sea island' - BBC News |url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-32331964 |accessdate = 2015-05-22 |archive-date = 2015-05-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150526230612/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-32331964 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

中华人民共和国不是在此爭議地區進行填海造陸的唯一声索方，但其他声索方的在規模上均無法与其相提並論<ref name=越南填海>{{cite news|title=越南也在南海填海造陸 前後對比差很大|url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1774507|accessdate=2018-03-07|agency=[[自由時報|自由時報]]|date=2016-07-25|archive-date=2018-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180308041347/http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1774507|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[越南|越南]]早於中國進行填海造陸，在其控制的[[西礁|西礁]]與[[敦謙沙洲|敦謙沙洲]]（越南稱山歌島）新增分別约6.5万[[平方米|平方米]]與2.1万平方米的土地；而中國在[[永暑礁|永暑礁]]一年就已經造出90万平方米的土地<ref name=德國之聲>{{cite news|title=填海造地--越南与中国"赛跑"？|url=http://www.dw.de/%E5%A1%AB%E6%B5%B7%E9%80%A0%E5%9C%B0-%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E8%B5%9B%E8%B7%91/a-18438612|accessdate=2015-05-22|agency=[[德國之聲|德國之聲]]|date=2015-05-08|archive-date=2015-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150527081002/http://www.dw.de/%E5%A1%AB%E6%B5%B7%E9%80%A0%E5%9C%B0-%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E8%B5%9B%E8%B7%91/a-18438612|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[中華民國|中華民國]]也曾在其實際控制的[[太平島|太平島]]進行幾次小規模擴建工程<ref name="Mira Rapp-Hooper">{{cite web |author1=Mira Rapp-Hooper |title=BEFORE AND AFTER: THE SOUTH CHINA SEA TRANSFORMED |url=http://amti.csis.org/before-and-after-the-south-china-sea-transformed/ |publisher=ASIA MARITIME TRANSPARENCY INITIATIVE |accessdate=2015-05-22 |language=en |date=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2015-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150527083330/http://amti.csis.org/before-and-after-the-south-china-sea-transformed/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 事件 ==
[[File:US_Navy_030615-N-0905V-006_Aerial_view_of_the_guided_missile_destroyer_USS_Lassen_(DDG_82)_part_of_USS_Carl_Vinson_(CVN_70)_Carrier_Strike_Force.jpg|thumb]]已到達[[渚碧礁|渚碧礁]]12[[海浬|海浬]]範圍（拉森号驱逐舰）]]

2015年5月，中美兩國在該區域發生了對峙事件。美國海軍的[[P-8波賽頓海上巡邏機|P-8A偵察機]]遭到[[中国人民解放军海军|中国人民解放军海军]]的警告而離去<ref>{{Cite web|title = Exclusive: China warns U.S. surveillance plane|url = http://www.cnn.com/2015/05/20/politics/south-china-sea-navy-flight/index.html|accessdate = 22 May 2015|last = Sciutto|first = Jim|date = 21 May 2015|publisher = CNN|archive-date = 2015-05-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150523014014/http://www.cnn.com/2015/05/20/politics/south-china-sea-navy-flight/index.html|dead-url = no}}</ref> 。中國政府稱，自己有權為了維護[[主權|主權]]，與防止海上事故，而行使一切權利；美國則稱，南中國海爭議地區目前於[[國際法|國際法]]屬於國際水域，美軍有在該區域通過的使用自由，美軍也將持續在該區域進行監測與飛航等的一切合法作為<ref>{{cite news|title=South China Sea: China's navy told US spy plane flying over islands to leave 'eight times', CNN reports|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-05-22/us-spy-plane-in-south-china-sea-warned-to-leave-by-china/6488690|accessdate=22 May 2015|publisher=Australian Broadcasting Corporation|date=2015-05-22|archive-date=2015-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150521215714/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-05-22/us-spy-plane-in-south-china-sea-warned-to-leave-by-china/6488690|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=AFP />。

2015年10月，[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]證實，美國將再次派遣軍艦或軍機進入此區域<ref name=VOA20151024>{{cite news|title=美舰近日或进入南中国海中国人造岛礁附近水域|url=http://www.voachinese.com/content/voa-news-us-patrols-within-days-20151024/3021382.html|accessdate=2015-10-24|agency=美國之音|date=2015-10-24|archive-date=2015-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151025121700/http://www.voachinese.com/content/voa-news-us-patrols-within-days-20151024/3021382.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。27日，[[美聯社|美聯社]]等媒體引用不願透露姓名的美方官員消息，指美國海軍[[拉森号驱逐舰|拉森号驱逐舰]]已到達[[渚碧礁|渚碧礁]]12[[海浬|海浬]]範圍<ref name=voachinese20151027>{{cite news|title=报道:美舰驶入渚碧礁12海里范围|url=http://www.voachinese.com/content/us-ship-sailed-within-12-miles-of-china-man-made-island-20151027/3024395.html|accessdate=2015-10-27|agency=美國之音|date=2015-10-27|archive-date=2015-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151028012748/http://www.voachinese.com/content/us-ship-sailed-within-12-miles-of-china-man-made-island-20151027/3024395.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，中國外交部長[[王毅|王毅]]則警告美國，不要「無事生非」<ref>{{cite news|author1=Editor: Yamei Wang|title=China warns U.S. against making trouble in South China Sea|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2015-10/27/c_134754072.htm|accessdate=2015-10-27|agency=[[新華網|新華網]]|date=2015-10-27|archive-date=2015-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151028165303/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2015-10/27/c_134754072.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[张业遂|张业遂]]召見了美國駐中國大使[[马克斯·博卡斯|马克斯·博卡斯]]提出了正式外交抗議，中國國防部也證實曾派遣驅逐艦對美艦發出警告<ref>{{cite news|author1=Ben Blanchard and Andrea Shalal|title=Angry China shadows U.S. warship near man-made islands|url=http://news.yahoo.com/u-navy-destroyer-patrols-near-islands-built-china-012942916.html|accessdate=2015-10-28|agency=路透社|date=2015-10-28|archive-date=2015-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151029154218/http://news.yahoo.com/u-navy-destroyer-patrols-near-islands-built-china-012942916.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；不過美軍官員仍持續先前說法，稱該處水域美方有權自由通過，且美軍還會持續派遣更多軍艦與飛機前往該處「通過」，因為華盛頓當局已多次表明不承認以人工建立的島礁，作為領土主張的依據<ref>{{cite news|title=US to sail again near islets claimed by China: official|url=http://news.yahoo.com/us-sail-again-near-islets-claimed-china-official-205029625.html|accessdate=2015-10-28|agency=法新社|date=2015-10-28|archive-date=2015-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031100351/http://news.yahoo.com/us-sail-again-near-islets-claimed-china-official-205029625.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

