== 立場 ==
中國政府稱，在該區域的工程大多是基於民用的需求，軍事設施的部分僅為滿足基本防禦。中國的目標是計畫在該區域建造[[住房|住房]]，及能提供[[天氣預報|天氣預報]]，和為各國[[漁船|漁船]]協助[[導航|導航]]的系統<ref>{{Cite web|title = China Voice: Drop fearmongering over South China Sea- Xinhua {{!}} English.news.cn|url = http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2015-04/16/c_134157325.htm|website = news.xinhuanet.com|accessdate = 2015-05-22|date = 16 April 2015|archive-date = 2015-05-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150528180646/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2015-04/16/c_134157325.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref> 。

根據[[美國海軍|美國海軍]]的說法，中國在2015前半年已陸續完成了新土地的建設工程，面積已超過了4平方公里，而且還在增加中<ref>{{Cite web|title = China building 'great wall of sand' in South China Sea - BBC News|url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-32126840|accessdate = 2015-05-22|publisher = BBC|date = 1 April 2015|archive-date = 2015-04-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150405051054/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-32126840|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = US Navy: Beijing creating a 'great wall of sand' in South China Sea|url = http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/31/china-great-wall-sand-spratlys-us-navy|website = The Guardian|accessdate = 2015-05-22|first = |last = |date = 31 March 2015|archive-date = 2015-05-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150522105803/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/31/china-great-wall-sand-spratlys-us-navy|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = China building a ‘great wall of sand’ in South China Sea– US Navy|url = http://rt.com/news/245717-china-great-wall-us/|accessdate = 2015-05-22|website = RT|date = 31 March 2015|archive-date = 2015-05-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150522115703/http://rt.com/news/245717-china-great-wall-us/|dead-url = no}}</ref>，美國不承認中國在該區域擁有主權<ref name=AFP>{{cite news|title=US planes keep distance from Chinese 'islands' -- for now|url=https://au.news.yahoo.com/world/a/28190990/us-planes-keep-distance-from-chinese-islands-for-now/|accessdate=2015-05-22|agency=[[AFP|AFP]]|date=2015-05-22|language=en}}</ref>，不过美国总统[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]在2015年6月1日表示中国对南海的一些主权宣称也许合法<ref>{{cite news|title=Obama: land reclamation projects in South China Sea 'counterproductive'|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/06/01/us-usa-china-reclamation-idUSKBN0OH38K20150601|accessdate=2015-06-02|agency=[[路透社|路透社]]|date=2015-06-01|language=en|archive-date=2015-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015134139/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/06/01/us-usa-china-reclamation-idUSKBN0OH38K20150601|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=奥巴马声称反对任何一方在南海填海造陆|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20150602/43891835_0.shtml|accessdate=2015-06-02|agency=[[凤凰卫视|凤凰卫视]]|date=2015-06-02|archive-date=2015-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150602130121/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20150602/43891835_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[东南亚国家联盟|东南亚国家联盟]]（ASEAN）稱，在此區域的大規模建設工程可能會破壞此地的和平、安全與穩定；而且如此大規模的開發將覆蓋珊瑚礁，對當地的[[海洋|海洋]]生態與[[漁業|漁業]]帶來災難<ref>{{Cite web|title = Why the world is wary of China's 'great wall of sand' - CNN.com|url = http://www.cnn.com/2015/05/14/opinions/china-great-wall-sand-spratly/index.html|website = CNN|accessdate = 2015-05-22|date = 14 May 2015|last = Schofield|first = Clive|archive-date = 2015-05-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150521045127/http://www.cnn.com/2015/05/14/opinions/china-great-wall-sand-spratly/index.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

